  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1112370/extras/abda3f7a2f164c20062a407f05634be3.avif?t=1728031073\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story begin when the robot, whose experiment was interrupted, begins working again years later in an abandoned laboratory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete challenging trails and puzzles. Explore venues reflecting different periods. Earn achievements by finding hidden rooms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the scenario and review your world ranking according to the time it takes to finish the chapters, compete with your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defuse the guard robots using the teleportation capability of the crystals. Complete the parkour before they die by being agile, solve difficult puzzles and try to escape from the lab.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can teleport to a certain point using the teleportation power obtained from the teleportation crystal. Solve puzzles and discover stories using a limited number of teleportation crystals in each section.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1112370/extras/42fbc6ddcb2ac38628e2c15e2b19f1fd.avif?t=1728031073\" width=600 height=1017 /></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1112370/extras/abda3f7a2f164c20062a407f05634be3.avif?t=1728031073\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The story begin when the robot, whose experiment was interrupted, begins working again years later in an abandoned laboratory. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete challenging trails and puzzles. Explore venues reflecting different periods. Earn achievements by finding hidden rooms.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play the scenario and review your world ranking according to the time it takes to finish the chapters, compete with your opponents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defuse the guard robots using the teleportation capability of the crystals. Complete the parkour before they die by being agile, solve difficult puzzles and try to escape from the lab.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can teleport to a certain point using the teleportation power obtained from the teleportation crystal. Solve puzzles and discover stories using a limited number of teleportation crystals in each section.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1112370/extras/42fbc6ddcb2ac38628e2c15e2b19f1fd.avif?t=1728031073\" width=600 height=1017 /></span></p>",
